Package com.pom.crimson.api

Provides classes necessary to create an API Test and the classes that the test case use to communicate with the corresponding APIs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIAOctaControllerAPI
    AIAOctaControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to aia-okta-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    CdsControllerAPI
    CdsControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET calls to CDS end points which internally calls dynamics API to get data from Common Data Service API and receive response for the same.
    ContentActionControllerAPI
    ContentActionControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to content-action-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    ContentAPI
    ContentAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to Content Service API and receive response from same.
    ContentControllerAPI
    ContentControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to content-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    ContentRootControllerAPI
    ContentRootControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to root-controller of content Service API and receive response from same.
    GroupAdviceAPI
    GroupAdviceAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to Group Advice Service API and receive response from same.
    MasterDataControllerAPI
    MasterDataControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to master-data-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    MilestonesControllerAPI
    MilestonesControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to milestones-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    MomentsControllerAPI
    MomentsControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to moments-controller Service API and receive response from same.
    MomentsLogAPI
    MomentsLogAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to moments API and receive response from same.
    MomentsRootControllerAPI
    MomentsRootControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to root-controller of Moments Service API and receive response from same.
    UserProfileControllerAPI
    UserProfileControllerAPI class contains functions to make GET,PUT,POST,etc calls to backend API and receive response from same.

Package com.pom.crimson.api Description

Provides classes necessary to create an API Test and the classes that the test case use to communicate with the corresponding APIs.
